{"type": "article", "id": 61660, "title": "故宫联名系列又发布了宫廷吉服，宋祖儿代言美宝莲 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-03-01T06:04:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14102, "name": "故宫"}, {"id": 56992, "name": "VIVO"}, {"id": 56993, "name": "IQOO"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 91, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190301124703z7VFdgqZwYC3MB2L.gif", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"QDVB\"><a href=\"http:// https://m.weibo.cn/status/4344966656864667?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>迪丽热巴成为 Garmin 代言人</b>，</a>她在宣传海报中佩戴着品牌的智能运动手表。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124731Ck5Bw1xTi30uDYdm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"pchT\"><a href=\"http:// https://m.weibo.cn/status/4344609792093297?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>宋祖儿从美宝莲品牌大使升级为品牌代言人，</b></a>并且还宣布代言人同款睫毛膏在国内发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124804oTztQK5mHIkCRp1X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3><a href=\"http:// https://m.weibo.cn/status/4344973765552812?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">值得一看的 Case</a></h3><p line=\"R6Ze\"><a href=\"http:// https://m.weibo.cn/status/4344973765552812?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>设计师平台 ICY 和故宫宫廷文化合作发起“吉服回潮”活动，</b></a>由 5 个中国设计师品牌参与设计。此外找来新生代模特袁博超在故宫拍摄广告片。今天正式在京东开始发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124821ZdGbwCvAS5IV7mY2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.629630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124822f8dySYiZKT42ghaA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.899251\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124822tZADYxuK25EwMSkd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124822eps4HjQzkng0UWmq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.629630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124822AESYcZsibN24OQmq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124822JaOfy0Zsvl23LHXP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.629630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124823M5BtclYhvGkZA7H9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.629630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124823Ajqmayt0QRzD2esr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124823PWJ15Qvb7xsSK6Yo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"5.740000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"mbTp\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTg1MjM1NTk2MA==&amp;mid=2348035950&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=535ca82a6dc28f2581124513ea8b5ca0&amp;key=483299f3b4f7cf0a3e8d6d25845f1020fcd705319051fc65c6b081dc11cdf03e3405b4deb097121ffbd86293ead2c288888ada2e7b78e4040bc340a983855e41611ca0f5c8b9d1b65af7f18b730b4a84&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=cELfcGM1A%2BlfDZeYSafBd6u8U1GfEZd7XUWDMhWH4oNlyncqDFwOoccdE%2B93ai0O\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Nike 的上海女生节活动今天发布了正式的广告片，</b></a>网球冠军李娜出镜讲述面对周围的“指教”，打破所谓的分寸感。由李娜个人自传《独自上场》改编的电影《李娜》于 2 月 21 日杀青。</p><p line=\"mbTp\" class=\"\">Nike 今年在女性主题上的营销投入很大，前几天 Nike 陆续发布了单支女性运动员的宣传片，刚结束的奥斯卡广告请来小威来探讨女性主义。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=k08424ze516\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"mbTp\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8BhvpRJi5zE\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>日本手机运营商 Y!mobile 推出一系列搞笑广告《怪兽家族的忧郁》，</b></a>长相魔幻的父母担心要不要给小孩提供手机，不少潜在的安全风险让他们烦恼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=b0842xgyjdq\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"mbTp\">VIVO 旗下子品牌 iQOO 在 今天将公布第一款手机，<b>为此 VIVO 找来多位数字多媒体艺术家和创意工作对品牌 Logo 进行艺术诠释，</b>用视觉效果宣传新产品内在性能的优势。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p0843xsxyvv\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124909SjsuOiVlz3gP1JKY.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p><strong>关键词：觉醒|</strong><strong>平冈政展</strong></p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124908v5QyTa7eOgufpbr6.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p><strong>关键词：野性 |&nbsp;</strong><strong>Nicolas Girard</strong></p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124908abQq1jsLtAHDS9Jp.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p><strong>关键词：升级变身 |&nbsp;</strong><strong>茶山有鹿</strong></p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124909PUEY0klatWOTb4up.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562607\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p><strong>关键词：爆发 |&nbsp;</strong><strong>桥本麦</strong></p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124908SiIKpkG0WNu9wvFr.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p><strong>关键词：巨大能量 |&nbsp;</strong><strong>Haran Jung</strong></p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124909KWhg5ZAbRQkwqzEY.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p><strong>关键词：潜藏渴望 |&nbsp;</strong><strong>MixCode</strong></p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124907JqPuoGYsVchErZUa.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p><strong>关键词：monster inside |&nbsp;</strong><strong>Nidia Dias &amp; Martin Gunnarsson</strong></p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124909hPsej5oV4ymrYXt6.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p><strong>关键词：酷且有趣 |&nbsp;</strong><strong>SEENVISION</strong></p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301124910roGxnLSXysTqfCp1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p><strong>关键词：碰撞反差 |&nbsp;</strong><strong>Yambo studio</strong></p></figcaption></figure></div><p line=\"fCaR\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4344614107777100?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>沃尔沃赞助了高晓松新综艺节目《大城晓聚》，</b></a>不过不单是品牌冠名，高晓松将会和局座张召忠、林依轮、朱丹和徐根宝在沃尔沃车内聊天。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=s0843kll0f8\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"lCB9\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/aCAmRZ9Kozo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Spotify 昨天正式登陆印度，品牌宣传片融合了印度传统曲风和低音动感节奏，</b></a>着重展现音乐带来的不同用户体验以及针对当地做出的个性化调整。代理商来自李奥贝纳印度。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=v0843inu9ad\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"yjTg\"><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/creative-works/project/spark-visit-florida-sunshine-line\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国佛罗里达州旅游局和多伦多的 TTC 1 地铁线和合作推出一条“阳光路线”。</b></a> TTC 1 地铁线和佛罗里达州形状巧妙一模一样，又进入了冬季。乘客乘坐粉红色的多伦多地铁可以假装在佛罗里达，还把其中九个站名改成了佛罗里达城市的名字，地铁站内也布置成温暖热情的场景。代理商是 Spark。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301125047qeZ5rDsdIEuMLRxS.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.823438\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301125048eJV8qUB6OTKr3N0R.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732031\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301125047XmbdPhgo3yqckeIC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.531250\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903011250489GQhazvESb1WKHjC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301125048xtFLNbyZWzhnV69A.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745704\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301125049kte6fLVHNRKUcDBs.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628906\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190301125047kP2LIbEgAdtKlUMs.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"HoST\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/3OV4aKuh7jpBfY5Hyz-baQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>耐克中国昨天宣布将成为英雄联盟职业联赛（League of Legends Pro League, 以下简称 LPL）官方独家鞋服合作伙伴，</b></a>合作时间为 2019 年到 2022 年。面向 LPL 粉丝的鞋服产品也将逐渐面世。</p><p line=\"nIIc\"><a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/amazon-just-opened-up-ads-within-its-instacart-killer-amazonfresh-to-win-over-big-packaged-goods-brands-2019-2?r=US&amp;IR=T\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>亚马逊生鲜电商 AmazonFresh 现在可以让广告客户在搜索结果页面和产品详情页面投放广告。</b></a>不过广告只会向有能力购买相应商品的用户展示，并且可以定向到是品牌的新消费者还是回头客。AmazonFresh 主要是吸引高端商品品牌来投放广告，周四雀巢旗下矿泉水品牌圣培露的广告出现在搜索结果顶部。</p><p line=\"nIIc\" class=\"\">题图来自：VIVO</p>"}